# papers/ holds source PDFs and supplements (copyrighted publisher
# content) and per-paper verification.md notes (local audit
# scratchpads). The whole directory is local-only; nothing under
# papers/ is tracked.
papers/

# notes/ holds local audit scratchpads (verification + spotcheck .R
# scripts plus their .out dumps). They depend on the local papers/
# directory and are not tracked. Only the .md memos under notes/ are
# committed.
notes/*
!notes/*.md
